{
  "texts": [
    "It is imperative for future studies to broaden their scope to encompass additional regions characterized by diverse weather conditions, especially areas prone to cloudy skies.",
    "Examining the efficacy of different PV panel technologies across these varied climates could shed light on the versatility and effectiveness of forecasting models in differing environmental settings.",
    "Moreover, although we employed deep learning techniques such as CNNs, LSTMs, which have shown encouraging outcomes, there remains room for exploration of other sophisticated deep learning architectures.",
    "Techniques like the Transformer and Informer, known for their prowess in time series forecasting, present promising avenues for future work.",
    "Investigating these models could uncover new strategies to enhance the accuracy and efficiency of PV power forecasting models."
  ]
}